Jentah Sobott https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jentah_Sobott 0 Jentah Sobott is an Australian actress, best known for her recurring role in the cult television drama Prisoner as Heather "Mouse" Trapp. Sobott worked in theatre, before being given a role in prisoner initially as an extra, before becoming a regular cast member. She also appeared in Australian film. Jentah_Sobott is an_Australian_actress , best_known for her_recurring_role in the_cult_television_drama_Prisoner as Heather_"_Mouse_"_Trapp .
